title: What Knockout Lee Sin reminds me of:

embed.description: Per Wikipedia: "Popeye the Sailor Meets Sindbad the Sailor is a two-reel animated cartoon short subject in the Popeye Color Feature series, produced in Technicolor and released to theatres on November 27, 1936 by Paramount Pictures. It was produced by Max Fleischer for Fleischer Studios, Inc.

body: God I feel old. So, so old.

replies.body:
I watched this just then with no sound and was still a fulfilling and rich experience.
Thx for the link love you long time
